    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >About this game</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unscrew! Rotate! Analyze! Drop the octopuses and dive deeper into the ruins!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204880/extras/c9944440db00c43ab5f8a5f8316b5612.avif?t=1754658291\" width=384 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive deeper and deeper, solving puzzles with screws which will help you on the way down into the ruins! In “Screw Dive” the player will control Human &amp; SD.Bot  and explore the deep ocean ruins. Unscrewing the screws will loosen the stage and might result in a great collapse.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In order to dive deeper into the ruins you will have to use the screws to get rid of octopuses guarding the ruins. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204880/extras/f906f3edd7d7da7031168bc5cf358a1f.avif?t=1754658291\" width=384 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A simple un/screwing action game!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204880/extras/0b3990103e4d8aadbc137649796af92c.avif?t=1754658291\" width=384 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Unscrewing screws will loosen the stage, </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >be careful not to fall off the stage yourself!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It is said that there are some special screws as well…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Analyze the stage and drop all the octopuses!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204880/extras/4fbe55c2a9212cfd1bd96633b5d65b82.avif?t=1754658291\" width=384 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drop all the octopuses in order to clear a stage.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will only have a limited amount of battery life which means a limit how many times you can un/screw a screw.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >There will be a lot of missions and advancements, so be prepared to figure out the best way to clear the stages!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Characters</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3204880/extras/f3634bf8692b39286a5785013fe126f0.avif?t=1754658291\" width=385 height=216 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 《Human》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Human is a treasure hunter, especially for sunken treasure. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Together with its best friend SD.Bot, they look for unseen treasure day and night.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >One day, traveling in the ocean they find a mysterious ruin on the sea floor and…</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《SD.Bot》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >It resembles a driver and has a lot of stickers put on by Human, its best friend.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Mainly attaches itself onto Human back, waiting for the moment it might come handy.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Its main downside is that without battery it won’t be able to move.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆Any unauthorized reproduction or secondary use which apply to conditions listed below is prohibited.</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-----------------------------</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Content which contain</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Intention to harm this work and/or the view or honor of a third party.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Violent, grotesque, or sexual depictions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Excessive support/disparage towards specific politics, religions, or beliefs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >・Anti-social expressions.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Any form of violating third party rights.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >These guidelines are subject to change.</p>",
